---
import Card from "./Card.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" overflowAuto={true}>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold m-0 z-20">About Me</h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3.5">
        <p class="text-sm font-light">
            My preferred tools primarily are:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-sm font-light ml-6 list-disc">
            <li>PHP</li>
            <li>Laravel / Lumen</li>
            <li>TypeScript / JavaScript</li>
            <li>Vue.js</li>
            <li>Angular</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm font-light">
            Although I have a set of preferred tools, I prioritize selecting the most suitable one for the task at hand, even if it falls outside of my comfort zone. My ultimate objective is to identify the optimal solution for each project.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm font-light">
            In addition to coding, I also have a deep passion for gaming. I participated in the last ever Counter-Strike: Global Offensive tournament in my country, the VS Gaming League Masters 2023. I'm proud to share that my team secured a position among the top 5th to 8th teams nationwide.
        </p>
    </div>
</Card>
